 
<p>
Depending on your employer to pay for your trip to get an 
<a href="https://www.commondreams.org/views/2022/07/02/no-your-boss-shouldnt-determine-your-access-abortion-care">abortion
puts you in a very vulnerable position.</a>
<p>
In any case, I expect that only a tiny percentage of US workers
work in jobs that are covered by such commitments.  (Can anyone find
out what percentage?)  It's a nice gesture but it isn't a solution.

 